icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/bogota\/neiva\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your bus to Tatacoa<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n            <a href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\/pin\/create\/button\/?url=https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/88174&amp;media=https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/14165927\/colombia-3-week-itinerary-4.jpg\" class=\"block-pinterest\" title=\"Save this article on Pinterest\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n                <div class=\"block-pinterest__container\">\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__content\">\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__title\">No time to read now? <\/div>\n                        <div class=\"block-pinterest__subtitle\">No worries! Save on Pinterest to read it later.<\/div>\n                        <span class=\"block-pinterest__button\">Save<span class=\"visible-desktop\">&#xA0;to Pinterest<\/span> <svg class=\"icon\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg><\/span>\n                    <\/div>\n                    <div class=\"block-pinterest__image-wrap\"><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/14165927\/colombia-3-week-itinerary-4-19x30.jpg\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/14165927\/colombia-3-week-itinerary-4-376x600.jpg\" class=\"lazyload block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"Colombia Itinerary: The Complete 3-Week Travel Guide\" height=\"600\" width=\"376\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a>\n\n\n<p><strong>By Plane: <\/strong>Short on time? Consider flying from Bogota to Neiva (1 hour) and then taking a taxi or bus to Tatacoa.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-bogota-neiva\/\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your flight<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>However, if you want to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/sustainable-travel\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">travel sustainably<\/a>, you could take an overnight bus on night 2. This means you&#x2019;ll arrive in Tatacoa Desert first thing in the morning on Day 3.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary tatacoa desert\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary tatacoa desert\" class=\"wp-image-84572 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29123013\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-13-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair