"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h4 id=\"h-where-to-stay-in-tatacoa\">Where to stay in Tatacoa<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Tatacoa desert has a mix of lodges and glamping options, providing you with the real desert stargazing experience. However, if you want more accommodation options (especially hotels with pools), consider staying in the nearby town of Villavieja. From here, it&#x2019;s only a 10-minute tuk-tuk ride into the desert.&#xA0;<a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tatacoa-hotels-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all hotels in Tatacoa Desert<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/mana-star-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Mana Star Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/22115553\/Mana-Star-Hotel--450x338.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Mana Star Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/tatacoa-star-eco-hotel\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Star Eco Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\