much like the rainbow mountain in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Peru<\/a>). <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary hiking tatacoa desert\"><\/noscript><img width=\"242\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary hiking tatacoa desert\" class=\"wp-image-84547 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1376px) 100vw, 1376px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11.jpg 1376w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-430x600.jpg 430w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-581x810.jpg 581w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-242x338.jpg 242w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-22x30.jpg 22w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-117x163.jpg 117w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-129x180.jpg 129w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-550x768.jpg 550w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-734x1024.jpg 734w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-774x1080.jpg 774w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29113728\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-11-1032x1440.jpg 1032w, https:\/\/static.saltinour