_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cocora Valley<\/a>. Here, you&#x2019;ll find the world&#x2019;s tallest palm trees towering over green rolling hills as the mountain mist creeps in.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7.jpg\" alt=\"travel colombia itinerary\"><\/noscript><img width=\"259\" height=\"338\" alt=\"travel colombia itinerary\" class=\"wp-image-90053 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1469px) 100vw, 1469px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7.jpg 1469w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-459x600.jpg 459w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-620x810.jpg 620w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-259x338.jpg 259w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-125x163.jpg 125w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-138x180.jpg 138w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-588x768.jpg 588w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-783x1024.jpg 783w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-826x1080.jpg 826w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/09\/13111641\/salento-colombia-7-1102x1440.jpg 1102w, https:\/\/static.saltinourha