) or one of the shorter trails. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary salento colorful houses\"><\/noscript><img width=\"263\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary salento colorful houses\" class=\"wp-image-81930 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1494px) 100vw, 1494px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30.jpg 1494w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-467x600.jpg 467w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-630x810.jpg 630w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-263x338.jpg 263w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-127x163.jpg 127w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-140x180.jpg 140w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-598x768.jpg 598w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-797x1024.jpg 797w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-840x1080.jpg 840w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-1121x1440.jpg 1121w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-300x386.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-600x771.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-150x193.jpg 150w\" tempsrc=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30-23x30.jpg\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" onerror=\"this.srcset='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.src='https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png'; this.classList.remove('lazypreload'); \"><a class=\"pinit\" href=\"https:\/\/www.pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10173810\/salento-colombia-30.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Alternatively, you can also go horseback riding, which offers you a completely different perspective of the landscape. It&#x2019;s also a fantastic way to see the secret corners of the valley. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>As with all animal tours, always do your research to check that the provider is ethical and sustainable (an important form of <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/tips\/wildlife-tourism\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">wildlife tourism<\/a>).<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/salento-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best things to do in Salento<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28.jpg\" alt=\"colombia travel itinerary best hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia travel itinerary best hike\" class=\"wp-image-81918 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-721x1080.jpg 721w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-961x1440.jpg 961w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-300x450.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/10144132\/salento-colombia-28-600x8