dbye to the luscious greenery of Salento and head for the metropolis of Medellin&#x2014;one of the best cities to visit if you&#x2019;re backpacking in <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Colombia<\/a>! It sits around 7 hours north of Salento, and it&#x2019;s easy to take a direct bus there. However, if you want a shorter journey, you can take a direct flight from Pereira or Armenia airport.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary El Poblado medellin street art\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary El Poblado medellin street art\" class=\"wp-image-83885 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15145927\/medellin-colombia-44-683x1024.jpg 683w, 