tween 40-50 minutes, so it&#x2019;s a good option if you don&#x2019;t have much time on your Colombia itinerary.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-to-medellin\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Book your flight to Medellin<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Castle Museum medellin\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Castle Museum medellin\" class=\"wp-image-83904 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/15152810\/medellin-colombia-21-1-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-c