isty) neighborhood of Laureles. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/hotels-medellin\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">See all hotels in Medellin<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"products__container\">\n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/sites-hotel-medellin\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Sites Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/04\/25154341\/Sites-Hotel-450x300.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Sites Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                \n                    <div class=\"product product--block\">\n                        <a class=\"product__image\" href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/los-patios-hostel-medellin\/\" target=\"_blank\">\n                            <img class=\"lazypreload\" src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/build\/images\/blank.png\" alt=\"Los Patios Hotel\" height=\"300\" width=\"400\" data-src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/20090726\/lospatiosmedellin-450x281.jpeg\">\n                            <div class=\"product__content\">\n                                <div class=\"product__content-subtitle\">Accommodation:<\/div>\n                                <div class=\"product__content-title\">Los Patios Hotel<\/div>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-arrow\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-arrow\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>\n\n                        <\/a>\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-1080x802.jpg\" alt=\"best restaurants medellin colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"334\" alt=\"best restaurants medellin colombia\" class=\"wp-image-83796 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1080px) 100vw, 1080px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-1080x802.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-800x594.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-450x334.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-163x121.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-242x180.jpg 242w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-768x570.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-1024x761.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-1440x1070.jpg 1440w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-300x223.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13152807\/medellin-colombia-30-600x446.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\