n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>From the village, jump in a tuk-tuk to &#x2018;The Rock&#x2019;, a 10 million tonne rock that can be seen from far and wide. Steps are now zig-zagged into the rock (675 in total), so you can climb to the top for awesome views of the valley and the many surrounding lakes.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--tour \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--tour\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/guatape-tour\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your tour to Guatape<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/11104047\/medellin-colombia-14.jpg\" alt=\"colombia travel itinerary guatape\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia travel itinerary guatape\" class=\"wp-image-83752 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/11104047\/medellin-colombia-14.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/11104047\/medellin-colombia-14-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/11104047\/medellin-colombia-14-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/11104047\/medellin-colombia-14-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.