lls of northern Colombia. <\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>It&#x2019;s also the gateway to the ruins of the &#x2018;lost city&#x2019;, which are thought to be 650 years older than <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/peru\/machu-picchu\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Machu Picchu<\/a>. It&#x2019;s the perfect place to unwind, drinking coffee while you look out over the treetops and the coast in the far distance.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-575x810.jpg\" alt=\"colombia travel itinerary Marinka Waterfall minca\"><\/noscript><img width=\"240\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia travel itinerary Marinka Waterfall minca\" class=\"wp-image-88276 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 575px) 100vw, 575px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-575x810.jpg 575w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-426x600.jpg 426w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-240x338.jpg 240w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-21x30.jpg 21w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-116x163.jpg 116w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-128x180.jpg 128w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-545x768.jpg 545w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/08\/21165045\/minca-colombia-18-727x