ass=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-day-12-minca\">Day 12: <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/minca-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Minca<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On day 12, explore the sights in this natural paradise, including the blue lagoon and the Marinka Waterfall. Both spots are also great for a dip and are walkable from the village, although the hot temperatures of the day can make it a little harder. For this reason, we recommend using a motorcycle taxi to get around.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary minca travel\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary minca travel\" class=\"wp-image-87299 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/minca-colombia-5-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/11142458\/min