onal-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tayrona National Park<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>On the coast just below Minca, discover the incredible <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/tayrona-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Tayrona National Park<\/a>, a beautiful protected area that isn&#x2019;t dissimilar to the scenery you&#x2019;d find in the Caribbean!&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Tayrona national park travel guide\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Tayrona national park travel guide\" class=\"wp-image-85278 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/15174022\/Tayrona-colombia-10-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-