                  <p><strong data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Entrance Fee:<\/strong> 68,500 COP (&#xB1; 16 USD) during the high season. 57,500 COP (&#xB1; 13.5 USD) in the low season. Please note that you&#x2019;ll also have to pay mandatory park insurance, which costs 10,000 COP (&#xB1; 2.5 USD).<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6.jpg\" alt=\"hiking trail tayrona national park colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"hiking trail tayrona national park colombia\" class=\"wp-image-84719 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03123640\/Tayrona-colombia-6-683x1024.jpg 683w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads