d Playa Cristal (great for snorkeling because of its clear water!).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/tayrona-national-park\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Best things to do in Tayrona National Park<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Tayrona national park hike\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Tayrona national park hike\" class=\"wp-image-84706 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/07\/03122328\/Tayrona-colombia-7-120x