hose that are backpacking in Colombia. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary polomino beach\"><\/noscript><img width=\"270\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary polomino beach\" class=\"wp-image-82406 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1536px) 100vw, 1536px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4.jpg 1536w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-480x600.jpg 480w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-648x810.jpg 648w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-270x338.jpg 270w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-130x163.jpg 130w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-144x180.jpg 144w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-614x768.jpg 614w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-819x1024.jpg 819w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-864x1080.jpg 864w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-1152x1440.jpg 1152w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-300x375.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/20090606\/palomino-colombia-4-600x750.jpg 600w,