-cartagena\">Day 18: Palomino to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/cartagena-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Cartagena<\/a><\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>After a relaxing few days on the coast, it&#x2019;s time to head back to city life. This time, head for the colorful Cartagena, a city unlike any other you&#x2019;ll find in Colombia. Discover a place where every house is painted in the brightest colors, and street sellers wander with tropical fruit baskets.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20.jpg\" alt=\"\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-82054 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20-20x30.jpg 20w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20-109x163.jpg 109w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20-120x180.jpg 120w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/cartagena-colombia-20-512x768.jpg 512w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075717\/carta