vance). To get to Santa Marta, you&#x2019;ll need to take the local bus, which takes 1.5 hours. Once you&#x2019;re in Santa Marta, head for the central bus station. Buses leave for Cartagena every half an hour, costing 43,000 COP (10 USD).&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/colombia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Book a bus in Colombia<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11150050\/cartagena-colombia-11.jpg\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Getsemani cartagena car\"><\/noscript><img width=\"268\" height=\"338\" alt=\"colombia itinerary Getsemani cartagena car\" class=\"wp-image-82023 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1524px) 100vw, 1524px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11150050\/cartagena-colombia-11.jpg 1524w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11150050\/cartagena-colombia-11-476x600.jpg 476w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11150050\/cartagena-colombia-11-643x810.jpg 643w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11150050\/cartagena-colombia-11-268x338.jpg 268w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/11150050\/cartagena-colombia-11-24x30.jpg 24w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.c