ghborhoods, from the colonial houses of the walled city to the street art of Getsamani. After a day of wandering, make sure to also visit the famous Cafe Havana in Getsamani, where you can enjoy an authentic salsa dancing experience.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--mustread \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--mustread\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/colombia\/cartagena-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">10 best things to do in Cartagena<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075308\/cartagena-colombia-17.jpg\" alt=\"streets Getsemani cartagena colombia\"><\/noscript><img width=\"226\" height=\"338\" alt=\"streets Getsemani cartagena colombia\" class=\"wp-image-82049 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1281px) 100vw, 1281px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075308\/cartagena-colombia-17.jpg 1281w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075308\/cartagena-colombia-17-400x600.jpg 400w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075308\/cartagena-colombia-17-540x810.jpg 540w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075308\/cartagena-colombia-17-226x338.jpg 226w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/05\/12075308\/cartagena-colo