pinterest.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\" data-pin=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/13160849\/medellin-colombia-2-1.jpg\">Save<\/a><\/div><\/figure>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-to-colombia\">Getting to Colombia<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>There are a few international airports in Colombia. You can fly to the USA from Cartagena airport, and from Bogota and Medellin, you can find direct flights worldwide. The best flights arrive at <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-to-bogota\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">El Dorado Aiport<\/a> (Bogota), where your Colombia itinerary starts.&#xA0;<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--flight \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--flight\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/flights-colombia\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Find the best flights to Colombia<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Tip:<\/strong> you can also cross borders from Panama or Ecuador if you&#x2019;re already traveling in those countries.&#xA0;<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-getting-around-colombia\">Getting Around Colombia<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<h4 id=\"h-by-bus\">By Bus:<\/h4>\n\n\n\n<p>Traveling by local bus in Colombia is the cheapest way to get around. However, the country is enormous, and the distances can be very far between destinations on your Colombia itinerary. Because of this, we recommend taking overnight buses, so you don&#x2019;t miss out on valuable sightseeing days. Plus, you&#x2019;ll save on a night&#x2019;s accommodation&#x2014;win-win!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--transport \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.12go.asia\/en\/travel\/colombia\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Book your bus in Colombia<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bus.jpg\" alt=\"bus tatacoa desert\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"327\" alt=\"bus tatacoa desert\" class=\"wp-image-84620 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bus.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bus-800x581.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bus-1080x784.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bus-450x327.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bus-30x22.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bus-163x118.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/06\/29144938\/tatacoa-desert-colombia-bu