=\"noreferrer noopener\">Colombia<\/a> itinerary. However, generally, it&#x2019;s excellent for those who are backpacking in Colombia on a budget.<\/p>\n<\/div><\/div>\n<\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3 id=\"h-expenses-for-a-colombia-3-week-itinerary\">Expenses for a Colombia 3-Week Itinerary<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>A 3-week Colombia itinerary will cost you anything between 600 &#x2013; 2500 USD. This includes lunch and dinner, transport between destinations, entry fees, and accommodation.&#xA0;You really can visit Colombia on any kind of budget!<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-budget\">\n        <span class=\"block-budget__title\">Budget<\/span><ul class=\"block-budget__list\"><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hotels: 15 &#x2013; 250 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Hostels: 8 &#x2013; 100 USD \/ night\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--restaurants\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Price per meal: 3 &#x2013; 20 USD\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Transport: 3 &#x2013; 15 USD\n                    <\/li><li>\n                        <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                            <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--phone\"><\/span>\n                            <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                        <\/div>Sim: 20GB \/ 8 USD (Claro)\n                    <\/li><li>\n                            <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                                <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>Busses: 10 &#x2013; 40 USD<\/li><li>\n                            <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                                <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--transport\"><\/span>\n                                <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                            <\/div>Flights: 30 &#x2013; 150 USD (domestic)<\/li><\/ul><\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Budget tip! <\/strong>The currency in Colombia is Colombian Pesos. Save on exchange fees by converting your own local currency to COP with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Wise card<\/a>. You can use this card to withdraw money from the ATM in Colombia or pay by card at most shops. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/go\/transferwise\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Get a Wise card here; it&#x2019;s free!<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery has-nested-images columns-default is-cropped\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-i